CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 11, 1950, pg. 1. Headline reads: "First Baptist Church, Penn Township, Is Scene Of Ceremony Uniting Miss Gaines, Mr. Hollinger"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of woman from wedding party, possibly Marjorie Ellen Gaines or Evelyn Gaines Love, holding bouquet of American Beauty roses, posed in front of dark crushed velvet curtain, for Gaines - Hollinger wedding, First Baptist Church
